dmca.title: Pink Moon Rising
dmca.body:
Dear Mr. [Private],

We sent you on December 29, 2000 and on May, 03, 2002 a cease and desist letter requesting the assignment of the domain name www.luna-rossa.com to PRADA S.A., but we have not heard from you. 

We remind you, once again, that because PRADA S.A. is the owner of the trademark of LUNA ROSSA and of Luna Rossa
